Package: LGBTQsafety
Title: Safety Calculator for LGTBQ+ Laws (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andreea", "Zetea", , "andreeazetea@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package allows users to track safety for LGBTQ+ individuals around the world. Users can enter a country name and learn which local laws apply to LGBTQ+ individuals, as well as receiving a safety rating for this country. There will also be an option to receive information about social acceptance of the LGBTQ+ community.
